Package com.jakewharton.apibuilder

Classes which assist in marshalling the native builder methods to proper remote API calls and the resulting JSON to POJOs for RESTful APIs.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
ApiBuilder Quickly and efficiently assemble URLs which contain both in-URL fields and appended parameters.
ApiService HTTP method execution.
 

Exception Summary
ApiException Represents an exception which occured executing a remote API method.
